<i>We discover contestants...</i>

10:39.295 --> 10:41.214
<i>America's favorite TV shows.</i>

10:41.464 --> 10:44.510
<i>You've been chosen from</i>
<i>a long list of contestants.</i>

10:45.678 --> 10:47.054
<i>Meaning you've already won.</i>

10:47.888 --> 10:49.515
