15:40.585 --> 15:43.631
<i>My connection. He's</i>
<i>got unbelievable shit.</i>

15:43.881 --> 15:45.049
<i>Shit, righteous.</i>

15:45.508 --> 15:47.301
<i>We got this idea.</i>

15:47.551 --> 15:48.844
<i>What is it?</i>

15:49.094 --> 15:52.015
<i>We cut this stuff up</i>
<i>and double our money.</i>

15:52.265 --> 15:56.061
<i>Get a pound of pure and retire.</i>
<i>Know what that means?</i>

15:56.645 --> 16:00.565
<i>We get off hard knocks</i>
<i>and be on easy street.</i>

16:02.819 --> 16:04.237
What's the catch?

16:05.655 --> 16:07.990
That's red. I mean that's a red.

16:08.407 --> 16:11.954
It's not a red red,
but that's a red.

16:12.204 --> 16:12.913
Red?

16:13.080 --> 16:13.956
Yeah.

16:14.331 --> 16:15.666
You're telling me that's a red?

16:15.916 --> 16:17.084
I'm telling. It's red.

16:17.417 --> 16:21.548
