I want to know what's orange.

16:25.844 --> 16:29.222
Well, it could be...

16:30.850 --> 16:33.394
it's a little orange too.

16:36.230 --> 16:38.023
You know something?

16:45.073 --> 16:48.952
I always thought you're the most
beautiful girl I've ever seen.

16:50.036 --> 16:51.372
Really?

16:56.252 --> 16:58.462
Ever since I first saw you.

16:59.839 --> 17:01.508
That's nice, Harry.

17:08.056 --> 17:10.017
That makes me feel good.

17:13.271 --> 17:16.357
Others told me that before...

17:17.108 --> 17:19.068
and it was meaningless.

17:26.160 --> 17:30.540
Why? Thought they were
pulling your leg?

17:31.750 --> 17:33.793
No, nothing like that.

17:35.128 --> 17:38.298
I don't know or even
care if they were.

17:39.466 --> 17:41.093
<i>From them it was...</i>

17:43.387 --> 17:44.931
meaningless.

17:45.348 --> 17:49.560
When you say it, I hear it.

17:53.398 --> 17:54.858
I really hear it.

18:01.533 --> 18:04.702
Someone like you could make
things alright for me.

18:06.162 --> 18:07.580
You think?

18:11.418 --> 18:12.586
What is it?

18:12.795 --> 18:14.964
Remember I told you
about the store?

18:15.881 --> 18:16.757
Yeah.

18:17.758 --> 18:22.222
I've been thinking.
I put together some numbers...

18:23.890 --> 18:25.767
and it's not impossible.

18:26.518 --> 18:30.773
You could and should do it.

18:31.148 --> 18:33.568
We could do it together.

18:40.909 --> 18:42.327
What do you think?

19:46.856 --> 19:48.358
Stop already.

19:49.526 --> 19:52.905
