dress than a cheese Danish.

20:30.321 --> 20:32.198
Three things is all I
did to change my life.

20:32.407 --> 20:33.366
Three things.

20:33.575 --> 20:35.618
No red meat.

20:36.035 --> 20:38.329
Why do they stick in red meat?

20:38.580 --> 20:41.125
I ate red meat to the
point where I'd...

20:41.333 --> 20:44.503
eat it raw.
I loved my meat.

20:44.920 --> 20:49.049
You need to be passionate.
No red meat.

20:49.593 --> 20:52.554
No red meat for 30 days.

20:53.889 --> 20:56.725
Three things is all I
did to change my life.

