21:17.039 --> 21:18.290
This is not Madonna.

21:18.498 --> 21:21.461
Neither is this, but
I'm going on a diet.

21:21.794 --> 21:23.004
What diet are you on?

21:23.213 --> 21:24.255
Eggs and grapefruit.

21:24.505 --> 21:26.257
I was on that once. Lots of luck.

21:26.507 --> 21:27.383
It's not so bad.

21:27.592 --> 21:28.718
How long you been on it?

21:29.135 --> 21:29.762
