21:42.901 --> 21:44.611
Did you put her in a sweat box?

21:45.403 --> 21:49.325
She went to a doctor. With
pills, you don't want to eat.

21:49.909 --> 21:51.369
What's so good about that?

21:51.661 --> 21:52.495
I'm sitting here...

21:52.662 --> 21:55.122
not thinking about chopped
liver and pastrami on rye?

21:55.414 --> 21:58.459
You shouldn't talk like that
when someone's on a diet.

21:58.709 --> 22:00.379
Oh, big deal.

22:00.587 --> 22:01.922
I'll sneak more grapefruit.

22:04.091 --> 22:05.592
I'm thinking thin.

22:05.842 --> 22:06.927
The mailman.

22:08.303 --> 22:11.099
You have something
for Sara Goldfarb?

22:11.349 --> 22:12.725
I'm expecting something.

22:13.017 --> 22:16.020
Goldfarb... Goldfarb...
Sara Goldfarb.

22:16.396 --> 22:18.731
This is it? That's it.

22:19.275 --> 22:21.110
Wait, I got to get my stuff.

22:21.986 --> 22:26.073
Okay, spell out your name.

22:26.824 --> 22:29.828
S-a-r-a G-o-l-d-

22:30.036 --> 22:31.913
f-a-r-b.

22:32.205 --> 22:35.333
