22:44.927 --> 22:46.304
Alright, man.

22:47.305 --> 22:48.431
Here we go.

22:49.016 --> 22:52.603
Let's do this right.

22:53.103 --> 22:55.063
Come on, naturally.

22:58.442 --> 22:59.736
Come on, hurry.

23:00.862 --> 23:02.780
I wonder when you'll hear?

23:07.368 --> 23:09.455
They'll send you to
Tavern on the Green...

23:09.788 --> 23:11.582
where they send all the stars.

23:11.832 --> 23:14.835
I'll have eggs and grapefruit
at Tavern on the Green.

23:15.169 --> 23:16.295
I hope they have some.

23:16.462 --> 23:17.671
Hurry up.

23:17.880 --> 23:18.882
Here we are.

23:19.090 --> 23:20.217
Listen.

24:35.173 --> 24:36.300
There it is.

24:40.054 --> 24:41.139
There it is, baby.

24:42.557 --> 24:43.474
Shit.

24:44.058 --> 24:45.602
Shall we try?

24:46.936 --> 24:48.271
Wait, Ty.

24:49.023 --> 24:53.027
