so we know how much to cut.

25:18.764 --> 25:19.723
It's business.

25:22.851 --> 25:24.603
Fair enough.

25:31.361 --> 25:33.154
Sheet...

25:50.006 --> 25:52.384
Thank you.

25:52.592 --> 25:54.386
30 days is all it takes.

25:54.678 --> 25:57.556
Number two:
No refined sugar!

25:58.182 --> 26:00.101
Now sugar's everywhere.

26:00.309 --> 26:02.812
Even in bottled water.

26:03.688 --> 26:06.023
I was sick with sugar.

26:06.482 --> 26:09.736
It nurtured my spiraling brain
that I felt I was a loser.

26:10.070 --> 26:11.572
Juice by you.

26:11.863 --> 26:13.073
Juice by you.

26:14.283 --> 26:17.619
Rule 2 is no refined sugar.

26:17.953 --> 26:20.164
Don't even think about
sodas anymore.

26:20.498 --> 26:21.624
Sucking candies, very good, sir.

26:21.916 --> 26:23.668
Just stay away from that stuff.

26:25.295 --> 26:27.130
No refined sugar.

26:27.380 --> 26:29.592
For 30 days I'll eat right.

26:30.342 --> 26:31.218
I'll pick up my spirits.

26:32.761 --> 26:34.138
I am going to try.

26:36.932 --> 26:39.477
I found hope. And in that
hope, I found a way.

26:48.613 --> 26:49.739
Stop!

27:23.943 --> 27:24.944
Hello?

27:25.152 --> 27:26.278
Rosie?

27:26.487 --> 27:27.656
Yeah?

27:27.822 --> 27:28.657
Sara.

27:28.907 --> 27:29.866
Yeah?

27:30.033 --> 27:30.533
I need the number of that doctor.

27:33.203 --> 27:35.372
I don't understand why
you got to see him.

27:35.830 --> 27:38.417
Cut the son of a bitch loose
for Christ's sake.

27:38.668 --> 27:42.463
I don't want him telling my
parents I've stopped therapy.

27:43.422 --> 27:46.092
They're already pissed
off at me.

27:47.761 --> 27:49.805
I'm not going to sleep with him.

27:50.097 --> 27:52.432
I'm coming home after the concert.

27:54.393 --> 27:58.189
You're jealous!
Harry, jealous?

28:03.653 --> 28:06.364
You're stubborn, put
your arms around me.

28:09.159 --> 28:10.327
Stop that!

28:11.996 --> 28:14.456
I'll suck your eyeballs out.

28:15.583 --> 28:16.542
I'm disappointed...

28:19.129 --> 28:21.172
that you're indisposed.

28:23.508 --> 28:25.218
Is Anita out of town?

28:26.511 --> 28:27.805
