That's why I'm here.

29:10.685 --> 29:12.479
I've seen much worse.

29:12.896 --> 29:13.980
Thank you.

29:14.606 --> 29:16.149
How's your hearing and vision?

29:16.733 --> 29:18.194
I have both.

29:19.570 --> 29:21.656
The doctor will be
with you shortly.

29:29.706 --> 29:31.333
You're a little overweight.

29:31.667 --> 29:32.376
A little?

29:32.793 --> 29:34.920
I have 50 lbs. I'm
willing to donate.

29:35.128 --> 29:37.924
We can take care of
that, no problem.

30:29.397 --> 30:32.483
We're on the way, baby.

30:32.984 --> 30:36.112
It was great out there.
Everybody's thirsty.

30:36.864 --> 30:38.282
Come to me.

31:27.461 --> 31:29.046
Purple in the morning.

31:29.672 --> 31:33.425
Blue in the afternoon.
Orange in the evening.

31:35.511 --> 31:37.722
That's my three meals.

31:40.225 --> 31:41.476
And green at night.

31:42.227 --> 31:43.270
Just like that. 1, 2, 3, 4.

32:55.599 --> 32:56.976
Come back to bed, honey.

32:57.310 --> 33:00.063
Come on, got plenty
of time for that.

33:00.772 --> 33:04.150
I'm grooving with these
new mirrors I got.

33:25.423 --> 33:28.177
I told you, ma,
one day I'd make it.

33:29.095 --> 33:31.138
You don't have to make anything.

33:31.389 --> 33:32.932
You just have to love your momma.

33:37.437 --> 33:39.022
What are you doing, baby?

33:39.940 --> 33:41.066
Nothing.

33:44.528 --> 33:45.779
I was thinking about you...

33:48.574 --> 33:50.868
and about the nasty things
I'm about to do to ya.

33:52.036 --> 33:53.329
I'm going to get on you.

33:56.834 --> 33:58.377
You'll scare me to death.

33:58.544 --> 34:02.631
I won't scare you. I don't
want to scare nobody.

34:05.509 --> 34:08.679
All I want is a little
peace and happiness.

34:10.724 --> 34:16.397
You're the finest fox I
ever laid my eyes on.

34:20.025 --> 34:21.277
That's what I'll do.

34:22.862 --> 34:24.237
For my mother.

34:24.530 --> 34:26.324
I've been thinking about
getting something for her.

34:26.574 --> 34:29.161
Like a present, or something.

34:29.578 --> 34:32.956
But I didn't know what
I was going to get.

34:33.206 --> 34:33.956
And?

34:34.166 --> 34:37.253
I finally asked myself,
what's her fix?

34:39.339 --> 34:40.465
Television, right?

34:40.797 --> 34:43.092
If ever there's a TV
junkie, it's the old lady.

34:43.509 --> 34:46.722
I owe her a new set anyway
after...

34:46.931 --> 34:49.934
being schlepped around
to old Abe's.

34:50.643 --> 34:51.810
You really love her.

34:55.438 --> 34:57.233
I guess so.

35:01.029 --> 35:03.198
I just want her to be happy.

35:03.448 --> 35:04.616
Let's go get it.

35:08.037 --> 35:09.538
Let's push-off first.

35:13.209 --> 35:16.129
We shouldn't get going
till tonight.

36:27.625 --> 36:28.626
Number three...

36:28.959 --> 36:29.918
Three!

36:30.210 --> 36:33.631
This drives most people crazy.

36:38.887 --> 36:40.847
This... is... easy... so... far...

36:41.389 --> 36:43.516
Give yourself 30 days...

36:43.808 --> 36:49.106
I guarantee... it will...
change... your... life...

37:36.033 --> 37:37.535
I mean that is thin.

37:37.618 --> 37:39.537
She doesn't look
like the same person.

37:40.162 --> 37:42.373
I can almost zip the dress.

37:42.790 --> 37:44.292
I've almost got the zipper up.

37:44.542 --> 37:45.669
Sara, the mailman.

37:46.086 --> 37:48.422
When I see it,
I'll wave it all over.

37:49.631 --> 37:51.300
- You sure?
- Yeah, I'm sure.

37:51.591 --> 37:52.801
What did he say?

37:53.010 --> 37:54.971
Don't worry, it'll come.

37:55.221 --> 37:56.389
He said it'll come.

37:56.848 --> 37:58.182
I once waited 2 months
for a package.

37:58.433 --> 37:59.350
Two months?

38:00.685 --> 38:01.853
It's Harry!

38:02.103 --> 38:02.895
Look who's here.

38:03.104 --> 38:04.063
Harry!

38:04.272 --> 38:07.359
Easy, you'll crush me,
for Christ's sake.

38:08.611 --> 38:09.987
Come inside.

38:10.321 --> 38:11.488
Hi, Harry.

38:14.868 --> 38:17.537
How are you, Harry?
You look so good.

38:17.787 --> 38:18.747
You want something to eat?

38:18.997 --> 38:20.081
No, ma.

38:20.332 --> 38:22.584
A little nosh or a piece of cake?

38:22.834 --> 38:24.754
I could go out and get some.

38:25.004 --> 38:29.091
I don't have anything in the
house, but Ada will have.

38:29.759 --> 38:30.968
You want something to eat?

38:31.260 --> 38:32.345
No, ma, nothing.

38:32.595 --> 38:35.307
Sit down. You make me dizzy,
for Christ's sake.

38:36.391 --> 38:37.934
Notice anything about me?

38:38.477 --> 38:39.936
Notice I'm slimmer?

38:40.729 --> 38:42.022
Yeah, I guess you are, mom.

38:42.314 --> 38:45.652
25 lbs. I lost.
Can you believe it?

38:46.069 --> 38:46.986
And that's only the beginning.

38:47.236 --> 38:51.532
I'm really happy for you.
But will you sit?

38:57.289 --> 38:59.458
Sorry I haven't been
around in a while.

38:59.792 --> 39:01.210
I've been real busy.

39:01.543 --> 39:04.088
You got a good job?
You're doing well?

39:04.506 --> 39:05.840
Yeah, real good.

39:06.091 --> 39:07.425
What kind of business?

39:07.842 --> 39:10.804
I'm sort of a distributor.

39:11.054 --> 39:12.180
For a big importer.

39:12.472 --> 39:15.434
I'm so happy for you.

39:15.726 --> 39:17.019
Mom, you're killing me.

39:17.311 --> 39:19.522
Have you been lifting weights?

39:20.064 --> 39:21.357
I knew you could do it.

39:21.607 --> 39:22.650
You were right.

39:22.942 --> 39:25.696
Maybe you'll meet a nice
girl and have a baby.

39:28.824 --> 39:29.866
I already met one.

39:31.660 --> 39:33.036
Don't go ape shit, alright?

39:33.287 --> 39:35.498
Who is she?
Who's her parents?

39:35.832 --> 39:36.916
You know her.

39:37.125 --> 39:38.876
Marion Silver. Remember?

39:39.252 --> 39:42.964
Oh, Silver, of course.
Manhattan Beach.

39:43.298 --> 39:46.093
He's got a house on the
esplanade. Garment business.

39:46.593 --> 39:48.470
He's real big in women's undies.

39:49.096 --> 39:51.890
And before you go bouncin'
all over again...

39:54.519 --> 39:58.189
I want to tell you
I got you a present.

39:59.190 --> 40:01.318
I don't want a present,
just have a baby.

40:02.193 --> 40:05.281
Will you let me tell
you what I got ya?

40:06.615 --> 40:09.452
You're something else today.

40:10.828 --> 40:12.580
Look, I know...

40:15.208 --> 40:16.168
well...

40:18.545 --> 40:20.547
I'm sorry for being such a bastard.

40:21.381 --> 40:22.591
I want to make it up.

40:23.216 --> 40:25.803
I know I can't change
anything that's happened.

40:26.054 --> 40:30.266
But I want you to know I
love you and I'm sorry.

40:34.355 --> 40:35.814
And I want you to be happy.

40:37.107 --> 40:38.984
So I got you a brand new TV set.

40:39.234 --> 40:40.778
It'll be delivered in a few days.

40:41.028 --> 40:42.529
It's from Macy's.

40:47.202 --> 40:51.539
Your father would be so happy
to see what you're doing for me.

40:56.379 --> 40:57.755
You see that, Seymour?

40:58.589 --> 41:00.466
See how good your son is?

41:01.592 --> 41:04.388
He knows what it's like for
his mother living all alone.

41:05.430 --> 41:07.140
No one to visit her...

41:18.987 --> 41:19.737
Hey, ma.

41:21.531 --> 41:22.490
You on uppers?

41:22.699 --> 41:23.366
What?

41:23.574 --> 41:25.160
You on uppers?

41:25.953 --> 41:27.329
You on diet pills?

41:27.621 --> 41:29.748
I'm going to a specialist.

41:30.082 --> 41:33.293
You're makin' a croaker for speed.

41:33.712 --> 41:35.630
I'm just going to a doctor.

41:36.006 --> 41:37.590
Does he give ya pills?

41:37.757 --> 41:39.217
Of course. He's a doctor.

41:39.426 --> 41:40.427
What kind of pills?

41:40.844 --> 41:43.305
A purple, blue, orange one...

41:43.596 --> 41:44.598
What's in them?

41:44.932 --> 41:48.185
I'm Sara Goldfarb,
not Albert Einstein.

41:48.477 --> 41:49.603
How should I know?

41:49.812 --> 41:50.980
The make you feel good...

41:51.314 --> 41:52.606
and give you pep?

41:52.898 --> 41:55.360
Well, a little.

41:55.610 --> 41:58.322
A little? I can hear you
grinding your teeth from here.

41:58.572 --> 41:59.781
That goes away at night.

41:59.990 --> 42:00.741
At night?

42:00.949 --> 42:02.075
With the green one.

42:02.284 --> 42:04.871
In 30 minutes I'm asleep.

42:05.371 --> 42:08.499
You gotta cut that stuff loose.

42:08.833 --> 42:10.251
It's no good.

42:10.543 --> 42:13.129
What? 25 lbs. I've lost.

42:13.463 --> 42:15.883
Do you want to be a dope fiend?

42:16.258 --> 42:19.386
Am I foaming at the mouth,
or something?

42:19.720 --> 42:20.596
He's a nice doctor.

42:20.804 --> 42:22.890
That croaker's no good.

42:23.182 --> 42:24.601
How come you know so much?

42:24.809 --> 42:27.020
How come you know more
than a doctor?

42:29.105 --> 42:31.066
Believe me, ma, I know.

42:33.819 --> 42:35.863
You'll get strung out.

42:36.364 --> 42:39.116
Come on, I almost
fit in my red dress.

42:39.659 --> 42:42.161
The one I wore to your
high school graduation...

42:42.870 --> 42:44.623
your father liked so much.

42:45.624 --> 42:48.418
I remember how he looked
at me in the red dress.

42:51.254 --> 42:52.589
What's the big deal?

42:56.386 --> 42:57.887
I'm going to wear...

42:59.430 --> 43:00.932
You don't know?

43:01.724 --> 43:06.230
I'm going to be on TV.
I got a call and application...

43:06.981 --> 43:09.191
Whose pullin' ya leg?

43:09.483 --> 43:13.947
I'm going to be a
TV contestant.

43:14.364 --> 43:16.491
I don't know when yet.

43:16.700 --> 43:19.077
You'll be so proud
when you see your mother...

43:19.327 --> 43:22.455
in her red dress
and golden shoes...

43:22.664 --> 43:24.250
What's the big deal?

43:24.458 --> 43:27.586
Those pills will kill
you before you get on.

43:27.837 --> 43:31.173
You drove up in a cab.

43:32.049 --> 43:33.969
Did you see who had the best seat?

43:35.095 --> 43:39.016
I'm somebody now.
Everybody likes me.

43:40.600 --> 43:45.481
Millions of people will
see me and like me.

43:46.733 --> 43:49.944
I'll tell them about
you and your father.

43:50.903 --> 43:54.450
How good he was to us.
Remember?

43:58.037 --> 43:59.997
It's a reason to
get up in the morning.

44:01.874 --> 44:05.879
A reason to lose weight,
to fit in the red dress.

44:07.964 --> 44:10.300
A reason to smile.

44:11.843 --> 44:14.430
It makes tomorrow alright.

44:18.225 --> 44:19.894
What have I got, Harry?

44:22.981 --> 44:26.401
Why should I make the
bed or wash the dishes?

44:26.693 --> 44:30.072
I do but, why should I?

44:31.573 --> 44:32.616
I'm alone.

44:34.285 --> 44:37.622
Your father's gone.
You're gone.

44:40.124 --> 44:43.837
I got no one to care for.

44:45.506 --> 44:47.341
What have I got, Harry?

44:52.721 --> 44:54.015
I'm lonely.

44:56.559 --> 44:58.144
I'm old.

44:59.104 --> 45:00.814
You got friends, ma.

45:01.064 --> 45:05.486
It's not the same.
They don't need me.

45:11.701 --> 45:13.787
I like the way I feel.

45:15.914 --> 45:18.667
I like thinking about
the red dress...

45:18.917 --> 45:22.337
and television... and
you and your father.

45:24.382 --> 45:27.760
When I get the sun, I smile.

45:34.143 --> 45:35.769
I'll come visit, ma.

45:37.438 --> 45:40.983
Now I'm straight, my business
is going good, I'll come.

45:41.608 --> 45:44.112
Me and Marion.
We'll come for dinner.

45:44.446 --> 45:48.450
You bring her. I'll make
you mushroom soup and a roast.

45:49.868 --> 45:53.164
That sounds great, ma.

45:53.956 --> 45:56.500
I'll call ahead of time.

45:56.751 --> 45:59.503
Okay. I'm glad.

46:01.380 --> 46:05.594
I'm glad you have a nice
girl and your own business.

46:12.769 --> 46:17.106
I got to go. I have
an appointment in a bit.

46:17.982 --> 46:19.233
But I'll be back.

46:19.442 --> 46:21.319
You still got your key?

46:21.527 --> 46:22.821
Yeah, I got it, ma.

46:25.449 --> 46:26.659
Goodbye, son.

47:05.535 --> 47:07.161
Brody say you coming up quick.

47:09.247 --> 47:10.498
Thanks, man.

47:13.460 --> 47:14.420
He says you're smart.

47:14.962 --> 47:17.006
You're loyal, and not a junkie.

47:21.218 --> 47:22.804
Brody wants to promote you.

47:23.596 --> 47:25.765
To give you more responsibility.
You interested?

47:26.558 --> 47:29.602
Yeah, yeah.

47:34.400 --> 47:36.986
Brody says you fuck him,
I'll kill you.

47:37.194 --> 47:37.820
I got that.

47:38.029 --> 47:39.280
Remember that.

47:42.993 --> 47:44.953
Shit, you got a white driver.

48:43.476 --> 48:44.852
I love you, Harry.

48:48.773 --> 48:50.566
You make me feel like a person.

48:53.487 --> 48:59.243
Like I'm me and beautiful.

49:01.203 --> 49:03.665
You are beautiful.

49:07.627 --> 49:11.006
The most beautiful
girl in the world.

49:12.967 --> 49:14.844
You're my dream.

49:21.434 --> 49:24.771
<i>No, Mrs. Goldfarb, I'm sure.</i>
<i>I've checked again.</i>

49:25.022 --> 49:27.858
Maybe you got me a weaker
one last time.

49:28.316 --> 49:29.776
<i>That isn't possible.</i>

49:29.985 --> 49:32.071
<i>They're all the same potency.</i>

49:32.280 --> 49:34.157
Something isn't the same.

49:34.365 --> 49:36.034
<i>You're becoming adjusted to them.</i>

49:36.242 --> 49:39.078
<i>It's nothing to worry</i>
<i>about, Mrs. Goldfarb.</i>

49:57.474 --> 49:58.808
We got a winner!

49:59.017 --> 49:59.809
We got a winner!

50:00.060 --> 50:01.269
We got a winner!

50:01.479 --> 50:04.857
A beautiful woman
with a magical smile.

50:05.232 --> 50:07.109
Straight from Brighton
Beach Brooklyn.

50:07.318 --> 50:10.404
Let's give a juicy welcome
to Mrs. Sara Goldfarb.

50:10.654 --> 50:12.532
Juice by Sara!

50:12.741 --> 50:15.827
Juice by Sara!
Juice by Sara!

50:16.161 --> 50:19.206
Juice by Sara!

50:30.968 --> 50:33.889
Tyrone C. Get your shit
together. You made bail.

50:34.431 --> 50:35.683
How much?

50:36.308 --> 50:39.311
Most of our cash.
You're up for consortin'.

50:39.603 --> 50:41.314
Shit, man.

50:41.731 --> 50:44.317
It's a war between
Italians and blacks.

50:44.901 --> 50:47.320
Sal is keeping the
shit down in Florida...

50:47.612 --> 50:49.531
until guys like Brody
are all knocked off.

50:49.739 --> 50:50.573
Sheeit.

50:51.242 --> 50:52.034
No one's got a thing.

50:52.451 --> 50:53.452
Except Big Tim.

50:53.744 --> 50:55.496
Shit, let's go see him.

50:56.080 --> 50:58.457
He ain't selling.
He only giving up fuzzies.

50:58.958 --> 51:00.042
What?

51:00.376 --> 51:02.754
He's hooked on the thing, man.

51:03.463 --> 51:04.965
I told him I'd give
him all he wants...

51:05.173 --> 51:06.425
but he ain't selling.

51:18.730 --> 51:19.522
<i>Number three!</i>

51:19.897 --> 51:21.191
<i>Number three!</i>

51:21.734 --> 51:25.070
<i>This drives most people crazy.</i>

51:25.738 --> 51:26.989
<i>You're not going to like it!</i>

51:27.364 --> 51:28.532
<i>This is easy so far.</i>

51:28.866 --> 51:31.161
<i>Give this up for 30 days...</i>

51:45.051 --> 51:46.343
You alright?

51:49.263 --> 51:51.266
Yeah. It was a bad dream.

51:53.185 --> 51:54.436
Want some water?

52:17.336 --> 52:18.379
Maybe we should dip now.

52:18.670 --> 52:20.882
Marion, I already told you.

52:23.385 --> 52:24.803
It's all we have.

52:25.136 --> 52:27.806
Tyrone is going to
score in the morning?

52:34.105 --> 52:37.358
I don't know.
It's a bitch out there.

52:39.652 --> 52:41.238
It'll be okay.

52:43.865 --> 52:45.450
It'll be okay, Harry.

52:50.832 --> 52:53.334
Yeah, I guess so.

53:01.176 --> 53:02.803
I love you, Harry.

53:42.221 --> 53:44.557
What's the problem?
The weight's fine.

53:45.349 --> 53:47.769
The weight's fine. I'm not.

53:48.978 --> 53:50.898
The refrigerator...

53:52.316 --> 53:53.358
Something wrong?

53:56.945 --> 53:58.447
Everything's...

54:02.786 --> 54:04.996
all mixed up...

54:05.538 --> 54:06.706
confused like.

54:06.915 --> 54:08.917
Don't worry, just get this filled.

54:09.125 --> 54:10.503
Make an appointment for a week.

54:20.931 --> 54:21.890
Well?

54:22.849 --> 54:24.518
Tyrone ain't found nothing yet.

54:27.437 --> 54:28.772
What are we going to do?

54:29.523 --> 54:30.817
I don't know.

54:31.317 --> 54:33.653
You have to do something here.

54:33.861 --> 54:35.905
It's your fault we don't
have something.

54:36.114 --> 54:37.281
What are you talking about?

54:38.032 --> 54:40.077
You were hot to
get off last night.

54:40.327 --> 54:41.578
That is bullshit!

54:41.829 --> 54:43.997
We could have had something.

54:44.206 --> 54:45.999
I'm going to sit around and...

54:46.208 --> 54:47.960
watch you push-off alone?

54:48.210 --> 54:50.004
Don't put it all on me.

55:01.475 --> 55:04.812
Don't worry, man.
We'll fill it up again.

55:05.771 --> 55:07.314
Things will get better.

55:08.357 --> 55:11.278
We'll fill the box back up.

55:19.077 --> 55:20.580
You want to hear the news?

55:21.497 --> 55:22.915
What news?

55:23.583 --> 55:25.752
You got good news and bad news.

55:27.962 --> 55:28.963
Shoot.

55:29.172 --> 55:33.218
Good news is, in a couple of
days, they'll be prime back.

55:34.678 --> 55:35.429
Really?

55:38.265 --> 55:39.058
Who told you?

55:40.226 --> 55:41.227
Angel.

55:41.436 --> 55:42.520
Yeah?

55:42.896 --> 55:44.814
Says Sal sent word...

55:45.023 --> 55:47.484
to let go a couple of
keys for Christmas.

55:47.692 --> 55:49.069
Not wanting anybody...

55:49.319 --> 55:51.989
wantin' this glorious season.

55:52.406 --> 55:53.532
You believe it?

55:53.866 --> 55:56.744
I did, until I heard
the bad news.

56:03.418 --> 56:04.252
Yeah?

56:05.087 --> 56:07.381
Price is doubled and you
have to cop for weight.

56:08.131 --> 56:09.717
At least half a piece.

56:10.009 --> 56:10.802
How much?

56:12.095 --> 56:13.137
Two.

56:14.263 --> 56:15.681
Two? That's fucking insane!

56:16.099 --> 56:17.350
What the fuck you gonna do?

56:17.558 --> 56:19.812
He won't lay no nickel
bag on you.

56:20.104 --> 56:21.730
Where we gonna get two?

56:22.689 --> 56:23.899
You mean Arnold?

56:25.275 --> 56:27.820
Your parents won't even
return your call.

56:29.781 --> 56:31.241
I haven't seen him in months.

56:31.741 --> 56:33.201
So what? He's still calling.

56:34.202 --> 56:35.328
I don't know.

56:37.122 --> 56:38.706
I don't know what else to do.

56:39.917 --> 56:42.461
This is our last chance
to get back on track.

56:42.711 --> 56:45.631
We won't have to scuffle
and make that freezing scene.

56:48.718 --> 56:50.637
We need the bread.

56:50.846 --> 56:53.515
Getting the money
is not the problem.

56:54.224 --> 56:56.184
Then what is the problem?

56:56.852 --> 56:59.020
Don't know what I'll
have to do to get it.

57:06.696 --> 57:07.697
Look...

57:08.364 --> 57:09.366
baby...

57:11.076 --> 57:13.579
we'll be back in business
in no time.

57:15.038 --> 57:18.834
We'll start moving again
and saving.

57:21.129 --> 57:25.133
It'll be perfect. Just
like it was. I promise.

57:29.680 --> 57:31.348
You'll see.

57:39.900 --> 57:43.862
I had the flu forever,
it seems like.

57:46.990 --> 57:48.533
Are you depressed?

57:48.909 --> 57:50.036
No, nothing like that.

57:50.328 --> 57:52.830
I've been really busy.

57:53.790 --> 57:56.918
I've been designing non stop.

57:57.126 --> 58:00.047
I'm glad to hear you've
been productive.

58:05.177 --> 58:09.182
To be frank, I was surprised
to hear from you.

58:13.937 --> 58:15.146
Something wrong?

58:15.522 --> 58:17.107
No, why?

58:17.732 --> 58:21.195
That's usually the case
when you get a call...

58:21.445 --> 58:22.905
from someone you haven't
heard from for a while.

58:23.739 --> 58:24.907
Everything's fine.

58:29.621 --> 58:30.789
Actually...

58:35.502 --> 58:37.045
I have a favor to ask.

58:43.386 --> 58:45.805
You smug fuck!

58:46.848 --> 58:47.765
What is it?

58:53.981 --> 58:55.149
I need to borrow some money.

58:55.482 --> 58:57.109
May I ask for what?

58:59.821 --> 59:00.947
Turn the light off.

59:01.364 --> 59:02.866
What for?

59:03.908 --> 59:05.452
Just do it.

